name: Death of Fredrik Gyllenborg
obverse: Bust of Fredrik Gyllenborg facing right wearing Order of the Polar Star.
reverse_inscriptions: EN KIÄR IHOGKOMMELSE AF DEN SOM FÖDDES TIL REDELIGAS FÄGNAD D·1223·IULII 1698·OCH DOG TIL DERAS SORG D·25·AUG·1759·
description: Fredrik Gyllenborg, (July 12, 1698 - August 25, 1759) was a Swedish Count, lord of Thor Arable and Hammarby.
